---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import OfferBand from '../components/OfferBand.astro';
import { serviceSchema } from '../lib/schema.js';
import { site } from '../data/site.js';

const title = 'Why Sell to NextKey Instead of Listing? | NextKey Home Offer';
const description = 'An honest comparison of a cash sale vs listing with an agent in the Bay Area. See where each one wins on speed, repairs, fees, and certainty before you decide.';

const crumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', path: '/' },
  { name: 'Why Sell to NextKey', path: '/why-sell' },
];
---
<Base title={title} description={description}
  schema={[
    serviceSchema({
      name: 'Sell Your House for Cash vs Listing with an Agent',
      description: 'An honest comparison of selling your Bay Area house to a local cash buyer versus listing with an agent, and the situations where a fast, as-is cash sale is the better call.',
    }),
  ]}
  ogTitle="Why Sell to NextKey Instead of Listing?"
  ogDescription="A fair, side-by-side look at selling to a cash buyer vs listing with an agent — and the situations where each one is the right call.">

  <section class="subhero">
    <div class="subhero__in">
      <span class="eyebrow subhero__eyebrow">Cash sale vs listing · The honest version</span>
      <h1>Why Sell to NextKey Instead of Listing?</h1>
      <p>Listing with an agent is the right move for plenty of Bay Area homes. For others, a cash sale is faster, cleaner, and far more certain. Here is a fair, side-by-side look so you can decide which one actually fits your house and your timeline.</p>
      <div class="subhero__cta">
        <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="#offer">Get my cash offer</a>
        <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href={site.phoneHref} data-track="call">Call or text {site.phone}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <Breadcrumbs items={crumbs} />

  <!-- THE HONEST FRAMING -->
  <section class="band band--cream">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="cols-2">
        <div class="prose">
          <h2>We will tell you straight whether selling to us makes sense</h2>
          <p>Most cash-buyer websites pretend listing with an agent is always a mistake. It isn't. If your house is in good shape, shows well, and you have the time to wait for the right buyer, the open market will usually get you the highest price. We would rather say that plainly than talk you into a sale that doesn't serve you.</p>
          <p>What we do is solve a different problem. When speed matters, when the house needs work you can't or won't do, when a financing fall-through would be a disaster, or when the situation is private and complicated, a guaranteed cash sale is worth real money. The right question isn't "which is better in general." It's "which is better for this house, on this timeline, with everything you're dealing with right now."</p>
          <p>So below we lay both options out side by side, honestly. Then we walk through the moments when a cash sale clearly wins, and we tell you exactly what you get when that buyer is NextKey: our own funds, proof of funds on request, and a local closing you can verify.</p>
        </div>
        <aside class="aside-card">
          <h3>The short version</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>List if the home is move-in ready and you have time</li>
            <li>Sell to us if speed or certainty matters more than top dollar</li>
            <li>No fees, no commissions, no repairs on our side</li>
            <li>We buy with our own funds, so no financing fall-through</li>
            <li>Proof of funds on request, local title-company closing</li>
          </ul>
          <h3 style="margin-top:24px">Not sure which fits?</h3>
          <p>Tell us about the house and we'll give you an honest read, even if that read is "list it."</p>
          <a class="btn btn--primary btn--block" href={site.phoneHref} data-track="call">Call {site.phone}</a>
          <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--block" href={site.smsHref} data-track="text" style="margin-top:12px">Text {site.phone}</a>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SIDE BY SIDE COMPARISON -->
  <section class="band band--surface">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Side by side</span>
        <h2>Listing with an agent vs selling to NextKey</h2>
        <p>Same house, two very different paths. Here is what each one really asks of you, point by point.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <article class="local-card">
          <h3>Listing with an agent</h3>
          <p><strong>Time to close:</strong> Often 30 to 90 days or more once you add prep, time on market, escrow, and the buyer's loan.</p>
          <p><strong>Repairs:</strong> You usually fix, paint, and stage to compete, and inspection findings can trigger more repairs or credits.</p>
          <p><strong>Showings:</strong> Open houses, lockboxes, and strangers walking through on someone else's schedule.</p>
          <p><strong>Commissions &amp; fees:</strong> Commissions plus closing costs can run up to 8 percent of the sale price.</p>
          <p><strong>Certainty:</strong> Deals can fall through when a buyer's financing or appraisal comes up short.</p>
          <p><strong>Closing costs:</strong> Typically split or negotiated, and they come out of your proceeds.</p>
          <p><strong>Best when:</strong> The home is move-in ready and you have time to wait for the open market to bid it up.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="local-card">
          <h3>Selling to NextKey</h3>
          <p><strong>Time to close:</strong> A written offer in about 24 hours and closing in as few as 7 days, or any later date you choose.</p>
          <p><strong>Repairs:</strong> None. We buy as-is, in any condition, and handle the cleanup and repairs ourselves.</p>
          <p><strong>Showings:</strong> One walkthrough with us. No open houses, no lockbox, no parade of strangers.</p>
          <p><strong>Commissions &amp; fees:</strong> Zero commissions and no listing fees. The offer is the number you keep.</p>
          <p><strong>Certainty:</strong> We buy with our own funds, so there is no bank, no appraisal, and no financing to fall through.</p>
          <p><strong>Closing costs:</strong> We cover standard closing costs at a reputable local title company.</p>
          <p><strong>Best when:</strong> Speed, certainty, privacy, or condition matter more than squeezing out the last dollar.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="sits-note">Want to see the cash side end to end? <a href="/how-it-works">Walk through how it works &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHEN A CASH SALE WINS -->
  <section class="band band--cream">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="eyebrow">When a cash sale wins</span>
        <h2>The moments when selling to us is the smarter call</h2>
        <p>For a polished, move-in-ready home with no time pressure, listing usually nets more. But the math flips fast when any of these are in play. In each of these, the certainty and speed of cash is worth more than a list price you might never actually clear.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><polyline points="12 7 12 12 15 14"/></svg></div>
          <h3>You need speed</h3>
          <p>A new job, a deadline, or a date you have to hit. We can close in as few as 7 days instead of waiting months for the market.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>The house needs work</h3>
          <p>Old roof, foundation issues, fire or water damage. We buy as-is, so you skip repairs the open market would demand first.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10Z"/><polyline points="9 11.5 11.5 14 15.5 9.5"/></svg></div>
          <h3>You want certainty</h3>
          <p>No financing contingency means no last-minute collapse. We buy with our own funds and show proof of funds on request.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M17.94 17.94A10 10 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9 9 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19"/><line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/></svg></div>
          <h3>You want privacy</h3>
          <p>No public listing, no sign in the yard, no open houses. The sale stays between you and us, start to finish.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/></svg></div>
          <h3>A difficult situation</h3>
          <p>Inherited property, foreclosure pressure, tenants, or divorce. We have handled all of it and can move quietly and quickly.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/></svg></div>
          <h3>You want to keep it simple</h3>
          <p>No commissions, no repairs, no staging, no months of uncertainty. One number, one closing, and the cash is yours.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="sits-note">If one of those is exactly your situation, we have a page for it: <a href="/sell-house-as-is">sell as-is</a>, <a href="/stop-foreclosure">stop foreclosure</a>, or <a href="/sell-inherited-house">sell an inherited house</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHEN IT MAKES SENSE TO CALL US -->
  <section class="band band--dark">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">When to call us</span>
        <h2>A simple way to decide</h2>
        <p>Three quick questions. If you answer yes to any of them, a cash offer is worth a look before you list.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__n">Ask 01</div>
          <h3>Do you need to move quickly?</h3>
          <p>If a 60 to 90 day listing timeline doesn't work for your life, a cash sale that closes in as few as 7 days changes the math entirely.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__n">Ask 02</div>
          <h3>Would repairs be a burden?</h3>
          <p>If you can't or don't want to fix, paint, and stage to compete on the open market, selling as-is for cash takes all of that off your plate.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step__n">Ask 03</div>
          <h3>Is certainty worth more than top dollar?</h3>
          <p>If a deal falling through at the last minute would set you back badly, a guaranteed cash close with no financing is worth real money.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="steps-cta"><a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg" href="#offer">Get my cash offer</a> <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg" href="/how-it-works">See the full process</a></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUST SIGNALS -->
  <section class="band band--surface">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Why our offer is real</span>
        <h2>What you get when the buyer is NextKey</h2>
        <p>Plenty of companies will give you a number. Here is what actually stands behind ours.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid--3">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="6" width="20" height="12" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><path d="M6 12h.01M18 12h.01"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Our own funds</h3>
          <p>We are the buyer, not a middleman shopping your house to investors. No assignment, no surprise third party at closing.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><path d="m9 15 2 2 4-4"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Proof of funds on request</h3>
          <p>Want to see we can actually close? Ask, and we will show proof of funds. The number we send is the number you get.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card__ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 10c0 6-9 12-9 12s-9-6-9-12a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg></div>
          <h3>Local and accountable</h3>
          <p>We are a Bay Area cash buyer who closes at a reputable local title company, so a licensed professional handles the paperwork and the money.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <p class="sits-note">One honest note: NextKey is a local cash buyer, not a brokerage, and we do not give legal or tax advice. We will always tell you straight whether selling to us is the right move. See what real sellers say in our <a href="/testimonials">testimonials &rarr;</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTERNAL LINKS -->
  <section class="band band--cream">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sec-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Where to go next</span>
        <h2>Keep digging before you decide</h2>
        <p>No pressure either way. These pages give you the full picture so you can choose with eyes open.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="linkrow">
        <a href="/how-it-works">See exactly how it works</a>
        <a href="/testimonials">Read real seller stories</a>
        <a href="/sell-my-house-fast">Sell my house fast for cash</a>
        <a href="/areas-we-serve">See the areas we serve</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <OfferBand source="NextKey Site - Why Sell" />
</Base>
